</p>

<div id="outline-container-orgheadline1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="orgheadline1">About</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline1">
<p>
I did my Bachelor of Engineering (BE) in ECE at <a href="http://pes.edu/">PES Institute of Technology</a>, Bangalore in 2011. 
</p>

<p>
Subsequently, I did my MSc (Engg) and PhD at the <a href="http://ece.iisc.ac.in/">Department of Electrical Communication Engineering</a>, <a href="http://iisc.ac.in/">Indian Institute of Science</a>. 
My advisor was <a href="http://www.ece.iisc.ernet.in/~nkashyap/">Prof. Navin Kashyap</a>.
</p>

<p>
I spent the summer of 2015 as an intern, and 2016-2017 as a research assistant at the <a href="http://www.inc.cuhk.edu.hk/">Institute of Network Coding</a>, The Chinese University of Hong Kong.
Since June 2017, I am a postdoctoral fellow at CUHK.
</p>

